flowchart TB
    N1["1. neo-zkvm-guest: Proof/evidence flow shows how a claim becomes checkable."]
    N2["2. Claim: This unit performed: Run verifiable transition | Emit public values | Reject nondeterminism."]
    N3["3. Witness or input: public batch input | private witness | shared execution core"]
    N4["4. Execution or check: replay deterministic computation inside the proof system"]
    N5["5. Public commitment: state root, public values, verification key, and proof digest"]
    N6["6. Verifier: neo-zkvm-host | NativeZkVerifier adapter | audit tooling"]
    N7["7. Accepted result: SP1 public output | state root | execution digest"]
    N8["8. Rejected result: reject proof, public output, or mode; state root does not advance"]
    N1 --> N2
    N2 --> N3
    N3 --> N4
    N4 --> N5
    N5 --> N6
    N6 --> N7
    N7 --> N8
